# ? Q1. How do I fill up my choice for various undergraduate programs?

```markdown
Allotment of Programs will depend on the rank of the candidate and the other rankholders taking admission in the specific IIT. Seat allocation at the IITs, will be done strictly on the basis of All India rank (AIR) and category rank of candidates and their course and institute choices. Candidates can choose from courses, branches and institutes from the given list in the order of their preference. Students are allowed to choose as many courses as they like and can add more courses, delete some and change the order of their preference, until they lock their choices. However, if students do not lock their choices by June 24, whatever choices they have made will be locked automatically. Please follow the link [http://jeeadv.iitkgp.ac.in/](http://jeeadv.iitkgp.ac.in/) for details regarding Counselling Processes.
```

