# ? Q11. Can I change my department post-admission?

```markdown
Students who do very well in their 1st year are allowed to change their department. Department change is made strictly on basis of cumulative grade point average (academic performance) at end of second semester. Branch changes will be made such that number of students in third semester does not exceed 110 percent of the sanctioned yearly intake for a branch.
```

